dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Depths shown by contours. Map shows international boundary, 1967 cease-fire line, roads, railroads, historic sites, UNRWA Palestinian refugee camp with population over 5,000, and Kinneret-Negev conduit. "Boundary representation is not necessary authoritative. The 1950 Israel proclamation that Jerusalem be the national capital is not recognized by the United States Government." Includes notes and comparative areas diagram. "801187 (B00581) 6-88."
